HEADWORD: Leapfrog
<hw>Leap"frog`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A play among boys,
in which one stoops down and another leaps over him by placing his hands
on the shoulders of the former.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Leapful</ent>⟦br⟧
